{#- KB stat band — the wave-2 HONEST market-stat surface (charter, plan §3d).

    RULE (bound): this band renders REAL data from the feed mirror
    (src/_data/feed.js → Supabase market_stats, SQL-computed) or it renders
    NO NUMBERS AT ALL. Never sample figures, never model-computed numbers.
    (The home page's live-data-band keeps its SAMPLE-labeled preview band —
    a wave-0/1 decision for the locked-grammar demo; KB/market surfaces are
    the production pattern and go honest first.)

    DATA CONTRACT with wave-2 lane (a) Feed & Ops — feed.marketStats:
      {
        computedAt: "2026-07-14T09:00:00Z",   // computation timestamp (Art. 15)
        city:          { stats: [ { num, lbl, delta, period } ... ] },
        neighborhoods: { "<stat_geo>": { stats: [ ... ] } }
      }
    `period` per stat feeds the Art. 15 per-surface period naming
    (round-2 grade finding 9: the notice names the ACTUAL period per surface).

    Caller sets: {% set statband = { title, geo, art15 } %} — geo: "city" or a
    neighborhood stat_geo key. -#}
{%- set _kbstats = null %}
{%- if feed.marketStats %}
  {%- if statband.geo == "city" %}
    {%- set _kbstats = feed.marketStats.city %}
  {%- elif feed.marketStats.neighborhoods %}
    {%- set _kbstats = feed.marketStats.neighborhoods[statband.geo] %}
  {%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
<section class="databand" data-sec="databand" aria-label="Market snapshot">
  <div class="databand__in">
    <div class="databand__head">
      <h2>{{ statband.title }}</h2>
      {%- if _kbstats %}
      <p class="databand__stamp">computed {{ feed.marketStats.computedAt }}</p>
      {%- else %}
      <p class="databand__stamp">live data connecting</p>
      {%- endif %}
    </div>
    {%- if _kbstats %}
    <div class="databand__stats">
      {%- for s in _kbstats.stats %}
      <div class="stat">
        <p class="num">{{ s.num }}</p>
        <p class="lbl">{{ s.lbl }}</p>
        {%- if s.delta %}<p class="delta">{{ s.delta }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    {%- else %}
    <p class="databand__pending">This band renders real market data &mdash; median sale price, days
    on market, active inventory &mdash; computed by database queries over our own Stellar MLS feed,
    with the computation timestamp shown. The feed mirror is being wired now; until it connects,
    we show you nothing rather than a made-up number.</p>
    {%- endif %}
    {#- Art. 15.01.A notice — REQUIRED on every stats surface, wired even while
        stats are pending (compliance lane, build/wave-2/compliance/
        rules-current-read.md: "Based on information from Stellar MLS® for the
        period (date through date)"). The caller's art15 string leads with the
        exact formula; real period dates render from the feed mirror. -#}
    <p class="databand__note">{{ statband.art15 }}</p>
    <p class="databand__credit"><a href="/ai/">Computed and refreshed by Everlane&rsquo;s own studio automation &mdash; see how this site runs &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
